title: Inside Kevin McCarthy’s secret promise to expunge Trump’s record
description: Donald Trump is angry that the speaker hasn't endorsed his campaign. To placate him, McCarthy privately vowed to hold a vote to clear Trump's impeachments. Now, that promise is coming due.
